cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CY 

This paper is about online-to-offline (O2O) recommendation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to extract implicit contexts, which suggests cs.CL as another possible sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with real-time recommendation, which may fall under cs.SI (systems and control) or cs.CY (computers and society).
